Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.39,0:00:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在路邊有個因生病倒地而呻吟著的旅行者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.75,0:00:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一個男人路過此地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.66,0:00:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旅行者並未向他求助  他卻坐在其身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.50,0:00:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連續不斷地對旅行者說教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.60,0:00:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其主題為「為了不得病就要過有規律的生活」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.05,0:00:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後就這樣滿意地離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.23,0:00:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個男人的名字叫「人類統合體」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.03,0:00:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後出現了非常漂亮的美女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.83,0:00:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用好奇的眼睛注視者旅行者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.81,0:00:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「不要光看著救救我吧」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.19,0:00:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旅行者奄奄一息地說道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.56,0:00:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是美女一臉不可思議的表情問道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.80,0:00:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「想要我救你嗎？」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.14,0:01:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後花了不少的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.42,0:01:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美女終於理解了他的問題  點頭而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.57,0:01:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久就帶來了一整座醫院外加醫生護士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.56,0:01:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個美女的名字叫「亞維人類帝國」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.14,0:01:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,選自行星米多格蘭特上流傳的政治寓言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.00,0:02:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs18\fnMonotype Corsiva}www.dmhy.net
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.00,0:02:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs18}動漫花園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.00,0:01:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fs18\fnMonotype Corsiva}www.cnseikai.com
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.00,0:01:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fs18\fnMonotype Corsiva}bbs.cnseikai.com
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.00,0:01:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fs18}特別鳴謝：幻炎28分艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.00,0:01:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fs18}壓制：alex
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.00,0:01:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fs18}校對：hirokifish ashitaka
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.00,0:01:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fs18}翻譯：ashitaka
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.00,0:02:04.00,Default,,0000,0130,0000,,{\a3}史法格諾夫門衝突戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.35,0:03:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.66,0:03:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0.9997的機率為敵方艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.69,0:03:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.15,0:03:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們應該在行軍時充分展現兵力了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.77,0:03:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  「非常地」充分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.75,0:03:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人沒有勝算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.55,0:03:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.76,0:03:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是理性的指揮官的話誰都會這樣判斷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.69,0:03:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.45,0:03:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何他們還在那裡磨蹭著不走？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.76,0:03:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0.9997的機率是敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.05,0:03:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的0.0003是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.89,0:03:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欺瞞情報  感知裝置類的同時故障
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.74,0:03:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未知的自然現象  或者未知的智能生命團體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.01,0:03:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  不用再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.81,0:04:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道閣下想進行戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.93,0:04:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡懷著疑問進行戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.72,0:04:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你認為他們留在這裡的原因是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.87,0:04:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一  是敵方認為能夠取得勝利的情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.90,0:04:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠勝利？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.17,0:04:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兵力相差這麼多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.51,0:04:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦的性能有可能遠遠超過我軍的預想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.17,0:04:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有調查清楚敵方的技術力嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.36,0:04:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您對喂貓的能期待什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.93,0:04:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  情報局和喂貓的是一個水平啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.54,0:04:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我認為情報局還是有點能力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.82,0:04:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個可能性幾乎不存在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.47,0:04:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果敵方自己認為會勝利的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.97,0:04:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那說不定要在敵方指揮官的精神狀態上找原因了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.23,0:04:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和瘋子作戰可不優雅啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.32,0:04:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二個可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.31,0:04:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們的主力是人類統合體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.05,0:04:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.38,0:05:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其軍司令部以時常發出有欠柔軟性的命令而聞名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.12,0:05:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以現有兵力死守史法格諾夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.07,0:05:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被如此命令的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.74,0:05:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這個區域集中兵力是最合理的作戰方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.09,0:05:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.40,0:05:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.77,0:05:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今我的疑惑如同衝入大氣層的宇宙塵埃般消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.90,0:05:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的內心離開了懷疑的岸邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.18,0:05:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到達了確信勝利的彼岸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.50,0:05:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡休爾千翔長    十分感謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.96,0:05:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的榮幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.55,0:05:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此那就不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.97,0:05:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備進行迂迴夾擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.68,0:05:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我反對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.73,0:05:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.29,0:05:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與敵方的距離太近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.56,0:05:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果在這個情況下進行迂迴夾擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.99,0:05:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會成為各個擊破的目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.35,0:05:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不至於敗北  但是會造成不必要的損失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.73,0:05:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒莉爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.38,0:05:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.78,0:05:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法  從正面進攻嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.42,0:06:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這才是妥當的作戰方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.29,0:06:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警部  康德林班對調查對象的搜查結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.85,0:06:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詢問下一步該到哪裡去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.11,0:06:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,編入友軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在決定出下一個方針前待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.65,0:06:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.42,0:06:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警部  是拉馬修迪巡查部長打來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.31,0:06:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像被佔領軍的關卡給擋住無法前進了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.95,0:06:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了啊  這已經是第10次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼就不能通融一下呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.44,0:06:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去  又該你出場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.03,0:06:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換我軍的指揮官來接
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.15,0:06:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.48,0:06:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0040,,還有3座嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.81,0:06:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.70,0:06:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.80,0:06:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  十分抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.80,0:06:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞維的小姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.44,0:06:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.00,0:06:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里姆澤爾亭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.00,0:06:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我放在這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.28,0:06:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.83,0:07:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其目的是探查深層宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.40,0:07:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們認為比起純粹的器械
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.58,0:07:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有機機械更有適應能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.54,0:07:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這便是亞維人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.62,0:07:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  亞維人不是人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.76,0:07:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是有機機械而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.59,0:07:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,味道淡了點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.09,0:07:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位自由的人類啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.71,0:07:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應當把亞維人趕回正當的位置上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.42,0:07:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即服務人類的生物機械這個位置上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.32,0:07:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這才是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.53,0:07:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,淨是胡說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.02,0:07:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的不是胡說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.81,0:07:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的祖先的確是作為生物器械而製造出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.69,0:07:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道這個嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.30,0:07:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.89,0:07:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.29,0:07:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們也不談及這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.89,0:07:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有書籍對此有記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.81,0:07:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是由父母傳述給孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.05,0:07:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,味道太重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.73,0:07:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.23,0:08:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次你的那份我會另外調味的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.12,0:08:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的祖先接受了母都市的命令開始了外層宇宙的探查之旅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.97,0:08:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在航行中發現了新的高加速源——「關閉的門」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.65,0:08:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此決定脫離母都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.34,0:08:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙深處獨立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.10,0:08:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.91,0:08:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.04,0:08:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後為了能在母都市派遣懲罰隊時也能安然無恙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.52,0:08:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,組織了軍隊  製造了武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.81,0:08:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  母都市不是沒有派遣懲罰隊的能力嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.50,0:08:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.67,0:08:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但即使如此  我們還是毀滅了母都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.77,0:08:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.75,0:08:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也問過父親這是為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.56,0:08:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據父親他說  是我們的祖先感到了恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.65,0:08:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們快要被那無法承受的恐懼給壓垮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.97,0:09:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深信母都市強大得無所不能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.39,0:09:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法理解啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.87,0:09:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對此也不是很理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.58,0:09:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是父親教我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.91,0:09:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身為亞維人就要背負著原罪和使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.90,0:09:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這麼認為的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.40,0:09:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原罪是毀滅了母都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.65,0:09:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使命是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.31,0:09:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保護並傳播母都市的文化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.19,0:09:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明憎恨他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.89,0:09:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對他們並沒有憎恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.44,0:09:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有的只是愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.01,0:09:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凝視著飄散在宇宙中的殘骸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.42,0:09:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的祖先領悟了這點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.25,0:09:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去睡覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.50,0:09:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.71,0:09:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.79,0:09:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.40,0:09:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對自己將要成為亞維人感到討厭了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.92,0:09:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.44,0:09:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經是亞維人了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.27,0:09:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是你告訴我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.52,0:09:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.27,0:10:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.59,0:10:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還有不明白的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.16,0:10:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  是什麼事情都不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.05,0:10:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我已經
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.27,0:10:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接受了作為亞維人這一新的命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這  這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.37,0:10:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.51,0:10:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,憲兵隊出動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.38,0:10:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喲  這可太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.41,0:10:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不要我們繼續搜索了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.18,0:10:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  發現潛伏地點後立刻向司令部報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.07,0:10:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,監視其動向並原地待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.56,0:10:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們無權逮捕他們嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.77,0:10:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對  將由我軍的憲兵隊進行逮捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.39,0:10:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.71,0:10:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們幹這幹那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.49,0:10:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到最後的關頭要我們乾瞪眼看著嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.11,0:10:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們所追捕的亞維人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.92,0:11:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是從平面宇宙進入的小型艇乘員的可能性增加了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.97,0:11:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.59,0:11:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且這個乘員可能是在平面宇宙中被我軍擊沉的敵艦的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.39,0:11:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣的話  可能會攜帶著重要的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.68,0:11:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的情報是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.88,0:11:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算知道也不能說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.52,0:11:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼  也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.92,0:11:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此  這個亞維人的價值就直線上升了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.16,0:11:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能抓到的話  人事參謀部也無法無視這份功績吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.69,0:11:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我總算懂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.71,0:11:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不想讓我們這種當地警察立這個功吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.44,0:11:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  是不想讓我立功吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.32,0:11:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.55,0:11:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是被選中的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.93,0:11:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼年輕就是上尉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.90,0:11:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年輕？我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.72,0:11:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警部  你認為我幾歲了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.11,0:12:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要做無謂的抵抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.96,0:12:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你  你們是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.55,0:12:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看上去不像警官嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.19,0:12:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警官...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.33,0:12:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個女的在裡面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.68,0:12:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞維的小女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.21,0:12:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  你們搞錯房間了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.03,0:12:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  去看一下臥室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.65,0:12:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.49,0:12:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢啊  真的是勇敢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.49,0:12:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你要是敢輕舉妄動我就不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.09,0:12:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是來逮捕我們的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.70,0:12:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,計劃好是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.35,0:12:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,計劃好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.46,0:12:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了  之後再說明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.40,0:12:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放開  這個臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.46,0:13:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.62,0:13:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很忠心嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.65,0:13:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過話先說在前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.09,0:13:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我們想讓你自己用腳走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.18,0:13:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也不是一定要如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有嘗過中麻醉槍的滋味？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.56,0:13:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼呢？快去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.65,0:13:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是亞維人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.05,0:13:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的在這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.84,0:13:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把  把武器扔掉  亞維人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.20,0:13:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就不管他的死活了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.38,0:13:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是麻醉槍  這個距離下也是能殺人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.14,0:14:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還是重新考慮一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.41,0:14:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,考慮什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.67,0:14:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果這個人死了的話你們也都會死在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.28,0:14:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰也別想從這裡活著出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.55,0:14:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先聲明一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.96,0:14:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在感覺特別差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.32,0:14:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為睡覺時被吵醒了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.82,0:14:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別開槍  我什麼都沒幹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.64,0:14:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  你能重新考慮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.87,0:14:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,考慮什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.97,0:14:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.99,0:14:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們真是沒用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是客房服務員嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.34,0:14:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.60,0:15:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是領導者瑪爾佳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.74,0:15:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是「反帝國克拉斯比爾戰線」的成員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.18,0:15:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種情形你們有沒有聯想到槍斃這個詞？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.56,0:15:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫  叫我葬禮社吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.57,0:15:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然另有本名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.12,0:15:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是同伴們都這麼叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.33,0:15:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫阿明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.62,0:15:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也有父母給我起過名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.67,0:15:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.35,0:15:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我阿明就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.76,0:15:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是比爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.96,0:15:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起飛車比爾的話這個城市誰都知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.33,0:15:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達斯瓦尼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.77,0:15:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你們能聽我說幾句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.28,0:15:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是為了你們好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.47,0:15:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是不是這樣呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.46,0:15:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「反帝國」的話好像是討厭亞維人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.99,0:15:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並不是討厭亞維人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.43,0:15:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是我們追求著獨立自主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.28,0:15:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否認帝國派遣的領主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.64,0:16:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追求用自己的宇宙船進行交易和探險的權利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.22,0:16:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.39,0:16:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帝國不可能會認可的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.75,0:16:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們在鬥爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.56,0:16:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鬥...和帝國？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.63,0:16:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我們是和什麼在鬥爭？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.10,0:16:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.21,0:16:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你們要怎麼為我們好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.54,0:16:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們成為人質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.92,0:16:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杰特  我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.62,0:16:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說得對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.74,0:16:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.93,0:16:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子你們可是會被抓住的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.44,0:16:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以幫你們躲起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.75,0:16:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到亞維人回來為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.50,0:16:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.64,0:16:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你們為什麼要這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.77,0:16:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿你們做交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.69,0:16:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.52,0:16:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  的確如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.24,0:16:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們想以這位小姐的人身安全作為交換條件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.49,0:16:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和帝國進行交涉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.45,0:16:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.85,0:16:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.51,0:16:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我們要提出條件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.70,0:16:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人質要提出條件？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.75,0:16:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.27,0:17:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先  我們不會交出武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.09,0:17:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶著武器的人質？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.90,0:17:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫你閉嘴啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.73,0:17:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有  我要一直都和她一起行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.48,0:17:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.88,0:17:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  做好準備就出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.27,0:17:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去換件衣服吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.52,0:17:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別把我當小孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.84,0:17:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的口氣太沒禮貌了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.92,0:17:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是侍從和貴族的大小姐嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.31,0:17:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是演技啦  演得還真像回事兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.05,0:17:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你們是以帝國收復這裡為前提的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.86,0:17:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果帝國不回來的話你們怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.04,0:17:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說亞維人被狂扁一頓後就縮回去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.58,0:17:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是今年裡聽到的最特別的意見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.53,0:17:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  葬禮社說得一點沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.97,0:17:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,羅凱爾  離預定位置還有120
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.06,0:17:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基提爾  全艦展開完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.28,0:17:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瓦卡沛爾 以完全停止狀態待命中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.19,0:17:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,維爾迭夫  隊列整編完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.62,0:17:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗杜妮  航向維持027
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.46,0:17:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴斯克·加姆留夫  正轉變為機雷戰陣形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.72,0:17:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵方時空泡分離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.67,0:18:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,0.9996的機率為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.68,0:18:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要管機率了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.39,0:18:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是敵方的機雷群
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.07,0:18:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.08,0:18:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.73,0:18:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.71,0:18:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,防禦機雷戰開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.03,0:18:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時空泡群開始接觸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.35,0:18:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方位305、距離65
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.20,0:18:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接觸範圍擴大中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.01,0:18:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機雷第一波  第二波時空融合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.91,0:18:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時空粒子已確認  機雷開始毀滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.86,0:18:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三  第四時空融合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.85,0:18:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵方機雷毀滅率0.831
