Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.32,0:19:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來自司令部泡間通訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.85,0:19:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朗讀本文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.96,0:19:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  「 進行蹂躪」  完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.77,0:19:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.94,0:19:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特萊夫提督雖然是第一次進行指揮作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.12,0:19:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻下達了這麼個簡潔的好命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.11,0:19:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第1至第6分離為單艦時空泡  轉入完全移動狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.18,0:19:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以戰隊為單位排成1縱列
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.37,0:19:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頂到艦隊的前方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.93,0:19:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.21,0:19:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本部戰隊  停滯狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.36,0:20:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發布集合信號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.87,0:20:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陣型為第3密集隊形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.03,0:20:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第4的動作緩慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.03,0:20:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭慢吞吞的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.96,0:20:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了  會自己跟上來的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.28,0:20:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以剩下的5個戰隊進行突擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.90,0:20:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.10,0:20:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.61,0:20:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向艦長傳令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.22,0:20:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全移動狀態  航向310
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.85,0:20:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連續發射信號「跟著我們」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.91,0:20:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵方時空泡接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.43,0:20:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.21,0:20:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這  這就是實戰嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.64,0:20:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是雖然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.15,0:20:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閣下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.44,0:20:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵方的機雷開始向弗杜妮集中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.07,0:20:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該進行防禦機雷戰了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.11,0:21:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的前任地是什麼地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.34,0:21:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在第184打擊戰隊擔任先任參謀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.74,0:21:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那麼可能你不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.91,0:21:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.07,0:21:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巡察艦上沒有搭載一發用於防禦的機雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.73,0:21:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巡察艦為數不多的機雷都是用來擊沉艦艇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.38,0:21:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點你好好記住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.09,0:21:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.19,0:21:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼但是不但是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.58,0:21:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巡察艦在這種雷擊下就慌慌張張的怎麼行？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.51,0:21:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是弗杜妮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.90,0:21:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到第1戰隊巡察艦邱爾維希號的泡間通訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.99,0:21:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本艦重創
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.46,0:21:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電磁投射炮及前方可動炮群無法使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.30,0:21:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退至後方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.70,0:21:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵方先頭集團進入迴避運動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.29,0:21:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要追擊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.56,0:22:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是傻瓜嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.17,0:22:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是在裝傻？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.29,0:22:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屬下失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.32,0:22:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在問你  是哪個？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.22,0:22:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個  是在裝傻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.80,0:22:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要這樣做？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.84,0:22:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為  那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.69,0:22:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在試探長官是不是傻瓜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.17,0:22:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.64,0:22:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼是為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.43,0:22:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉  正如閣下您所推測的那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.52,0:22:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這次就饒過你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.27,0:22:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是不要再犯哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.91,0:22:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後再犯的話就要好好教訓教訓你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.92,0:22:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會銘記在心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.59,0:22:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,維持目前航向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.58,0:22:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的目標只有戰列艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.66,0:22:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,護衛艦之類的雜魚還是給後面的人留著吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.92,0:22:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葬禮社說得對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.46,0:23:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞維人並沒有退縮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.46,0:24:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵戰列艦隊馬上就要在眼前了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.06,0:24:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再磨磨蹭蹭的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.38,0:24:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好處都要被弗杜妮給佔去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.45,0:24:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.95,0:24:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是死路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.63,0:24:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是舞蹈女神弗杜妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.57,0:24:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們看看我們的舞姿有多麼華麗吧
